pageProduct.description:
General Information

Resveratrol Max is a triple antioxidant support supplement that helps to enhance vitality, reduce free radical damage to body cells and support skin health.

Resveratrol Max 30s Can Help:
 Support collagen formation Help reduce free radical damage to body cells Support cardiovascular system function Support immune health Maintain skin health Relieve inflammation Support general health and wellbeing Promote vitality
Resveratrol Max contains antioxidants, supports vitality and helps maintain skin health.

What is Resveratrol?
Resveratrol is a powerful antioxidant found in the skin of grapes, red wine, red fruits, including mulberries, blueberries and cranberries, and some herbs and plants.

Size: 30 Tablets

Warnings

Always read the label. Follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Contains sulfites.

Ingredients

Key Active Ingredients
Reynoutria japonica root ext. dry conc. std
200 mg equiv. to root dry 20g (min)
equiv. to Resveratrol 100 mg
Vitis vinifera seed ext. dry conc. Std. 41.67 mg
equiv. to dry seed 5 g (min)
equiv. to procyanidins 39.59 mg
Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C) 100 mg
Contains sulfites.
Free from gluten, lactose, yeast, sugar, artificial flavours.

Directions

30 Film Coated Tablets Adults take one tablet daily, with food, or as directed by your health professional. This product has been blistered sealed for your protection. Do not use if tamper seal or blistering is broken or damaged. Store below 25°C.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C.
